<TEXT>
a prosecutor said ramon salcido was 
deported at his own request thursday rendering moot the debate 
over whether the admitted mass slayer would be forced to leave 
mexico to face trial in california 
salcido accused of killing his wife two young daughters and 
four other people left mexico city aboard the private plane of 
