crowded with hundreds of exhibits some still classified as top 
secret a us marshal guarded the door 
the foreman is a 34yearold hospital clerk denise anderson 
who said during pretrial questioning that she does not like news 
and that the extensive television coverage given norths testimony 
during the 1987 congressional hearings made me mad i did not 
look at it at all 
