threats that i have heard about were against official americans 
and werent general threats to travelers 
rowe was imprisoned in the jungles of vietnam by the viet cong 
from october 1963 until he escaped on new years eve 1968 he later 
wrote a book about the ordeal titled five years to freedom 
after returning to the united states he was made chief of the 
armys survival evasion resistance and escape training unit at 
