later served as commander of the 1st special warfare training 
battalion at fort bragg 
rowes decorations included the silver star legion of merit 
two bronze stars two purple hearts the meritorious service medal 
a national defense service medal the vietnam service medal an 
army service ribbon and the republic of vietnam gallantry cross 
