and forming the band that stayed with him on the gaia label his 
selftitled album in 1983 for pausa made the radio and records jazz 
chart 
the audience must have found us he said after that one 
record you hardly that i considered a bomb we started out 
playing a very simple kind of music still it built a following 
of record buyers and clubgoers 
