several corporate heavy hitters weighed in with 
their firstquarter financial results this past week and most 
figures tipped the scales close to where the companies intended 
a grim performance by rjr nabisco inc may have been expected 
due to its 25 billion buyout by kohlberg kravis roberts amp co but 
